      "id": "PopularPost219509",
      "post_content": "Banding is so flavourful, it would be a neat thing to bring back if only the rules/text were fixed.   \nSomething like:  \nBanding 2 (When you attack, you may have all creatures attacking form a band. Bands can only be blocked by the same amount or greater of creatures. Each (other) creature in a band gets +2/+2 )  \nA sort of Goblin War Drums kind of deal, with an added bonus. Would make great flavor of Red, Green, White weenie creatures.",
